name: Imbalance & Kintan Strider
Text: 'Cancel Blaster Proficiency. (Immune to Sense.) OR If opponent just retrieved Force, opponent must lose X Force, where X = one-half the number of cards retrieved (round down) to a minimum of 1. OR If opponent''s character just lost, lose 1 Force to retrieve the topmost character of ability < 6 (except a [Maintenance] or [Permanent Weapon] card) in your Lost Pile into hand.',
